snippet.title: Guildford Castle VR Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Get the free VR experience on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1862880/Guildford_Castle_VR/

VISIT ONE OF ENGLAND'S FIRST CASTLES, PAST AND PRESENT
Built in the wake of the Norman Conquest, Guildford Castle was one of England’s first castles and has stood for over 900 years.

Visit a hyper-realistic digital double of the castle as it stands today, created using state-of-the-art 3D scanning techniques. Step into the distant past and discover the royal palace and medieval town.

For all the latest information, follow us on social media: 
 - https://twitter.com/VrHistoric
 - https://www.instagram.com/historic_vr/
 - https://www.artstation.com/historic_vr
